      <div id="collapseFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">
        <div class="panel-body">
          <p>At the moment, the application supports users to create accounts and start their own surveys. They are able to send
            their own surveys and gather responses from their friends. Then they can see an aggregate of the responses they received, as
            well as each response individually.</p>
          <p>I have many ideas for features to improve the functionality of the application such as:
            <ul>
              <li>Better projection of the results</li>
              <li>Exporting the results, for more extensive analysis</li>
              <li>Sending invitations for surveys through the system</li>
              <li>...</li>
            </ul>
            You can follow the development of the project and access or fork the code on
            <a href="http://www.github.com/tassos/Johari" target="_blank">github</a>. If you have any ideas for new features, please
            let me know. I would love to hear your opinions and feedback for this application, so please don't hesitate to contact me.
          </p>
        </div>
