              <li>All your passwords are stored in an encrypted format on the database, so even if our system is compromised, your password is safe</li>
              <li>I am not planning on selling any of the data gathered, even if they would have any value to anyone</li>
              <li>I use a <a href="http://www.piwik.org" target="_blank">Piwik</a> engine for <a href="https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWeb_analytics" target="_blank">web analytics</a>. I am using it merely to understand where do my visitors come from and which pages are more visited. This way I can improve this service as more and more people are using it. </li>
